Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are resubmitted
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' after 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases where 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' grouped by 'org:resource'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource

Name: Total time since 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and 'Request Payment' are performed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in resubmitted cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
